{"tid":1884589,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【支那腦可防可控】支那如爆發鼠疫　知乎網民堅信政府：救援一會就到","createTime":"2020-02-17T16:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T17:31:08.000Z","uid":80567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a000ee54cfbd9328cbd5fbd9130acee504441957","tid":1884589,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"Link: <a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/30326059/answer/733116629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F30326059%2Fanswer%2F733116629&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbPcbRDcn212Q0H9cnoVtDxk%3D&h=c216e936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/30326059/answer/733116629</a><br />\n為免殘體傷眼，睇下面就得。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃字為笑點</span><br />\n<br />\n問題：如果遊戲中的《生化危機》發生在中國，我們該怎麽逃生？<br />\n<br />\n答案：（作者　小本本）<br />\n先發一段舊聞:2014年7月，中國甘肅玉門市發現一例鼠疫病例，患者於7月16日死亡。鼠疫患者於16日淩晨死亡，<span style=\"color: red;\">當日早上5點，甘肅省相關的衛生部門就已經接到報告</span>，並組織了省市縣三級專家進行實驗室檢測。<br />\n<br />\n當天，實驗室檢測<span style=\"color: red;\">還沒有出結果，就已經對玉門市老城區及赤金鎮進行了隔離</span>，約有3萬人被隔離，400余醫護人員、公安武警進駐，城區只許進不許出。<br />\n<br />\n市局同時緊急制定並下發了《&ldquo;7&middot;15&rdquo;疑似鼠疫疫情防控工作方案》，成立了疫情防控指揮部，全面負責<span style=\"color: red;\">防控工作</span>。<br />\n<br />\n17日，實驗室結果證實患者系感染肺鼠疫。同時，<span style=\"color: red;\">大量防護物資、食品</span>在當日淩晨緊急調往隔離區。17日下午共排查出與患者密切接觸者151人，實行監護隔離。<br />\n<br />\n同日，隔離區內公職人員開始對重點隔離區<span style=\"color: red;\">挨家挨戶宣傳鼠疫防控知識</span>，要求第一時間上報發熱癥狀。<br />\n<br />\n隔離區隔離時間為9天，因為鼠疫的潛伏期通常不超過9天。7月24日，城區解除隔離，保留對部分重點對象的監護隔離。<br />\n<br />\n這就是現代社會面對傳染病突發事件的處理效率。換做是只能通過體液傳播的喪屍病毒，大概<span style=\"color: red;\">不會掀起多大的波瀾</span>。<br />\n<br />\n所以呢&hellip;&hellip;就像上面軍警答友所說，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鎖好門窗在家玩手機就好，他們一會就到</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n哈哈哈哈哈哈哈，有歧義了，最後一句改成&ldquo;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">救援一會就到</span></span></strong>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>戇鳩支那人</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5e000afd1d237e1f83799ec2e6014ff523a9c090","tid":1884589,"uid":80567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"個答案係2019年7月發佈<br />\n啲評論開始有支畜返嚟笑鳩佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XWDBvuB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXWDBvuB.png&h=df12c230&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1caacfdcc4062773da9d3ac5cc068a6b1eec9a1f","tid":1884589,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RdKdxJq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRdKdxJq.png&h=4f282881&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n可防可控<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7803cc0e2dc178afa5f8e03e54215d6501641a6c","tid":1884589,"uid":101307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1caacfdcc4062773da9d3ac5cc068a6b1eec9a1f","tid":1884589,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RdKdxJq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRdKdxJq.png&h=4f282881&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n可防可控<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:31:08.000Z","msg":"似講反話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲就真係難分真與假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}